He don't just meet with anyone.

03:32.615 --> 03:34.474
All right, good,
'cause I ain't just anyone.

03:34.574 --> 03:36.113
Look, I'm serious
about my future,

03:36.213 --> 03:38.272
and I ain't afraid
to do the work.

03:38.372 --> 03:40.371
Tell him that.

03:41.610 --> 03:43.669
All right,
I'll see what I can do.

03:43.769 --> 03:44.908
All right, that's what
I'm talking about.

03:45.008 --> 03:47.187
Word.

03:47.287 --> 03:49.306
Stay safe out here,
all right?

03:53.204 --> 03:54.743
OK, I'm going to head out.

03:54.843 --> 03:55.942
Got to beat traffic.

03:56.042 --> 03:57.701
Mm, mm.
Well, have a good day, baby.

03:57.801 --> 03:59.140
Drive safely.

03:59.240 --> 04:00.979
- Have a good day, son.
- You know what?

04:01.079 --> 04:02.938
I think I'm going
to head out, too.

04:03.038 --> 04:04.178
Got to celebrate
my first day

04:04.278 --> 04:05.897
as manager
of the influencer house.

04:05.997 --> 04:07.656
I am so impressed
how you and Ivy

04:07.756 --> 04:09.055
just pulled this thing off.

04:09.155 --> 04:11.134
I mean, when we found out
Kylo was in debt

04:11.234 --> 04:12.613
and behind on his mortgage,

04:12.713 --> 04:14.092
we made him an offer
he couldn't refuse.

04:14.192 --> 04:16.491
