is going to be a teenager.

04:25.266 --> 04:27.085
Ooh, so many RSVPs
have been coming in.

04:27.185 --> 04:29.324
Everyone's so excited
for your birthday tomorrow.

04:29.424 --> 04:32.522
Ugh, Ash, Mum and Dad's
friends give the best gifts.

04:32.622 --> 04:35.001
- Oh.
- When I was 13, I got a horse.

04:35.101 --> 04:37.440
Actually, what happened to him?
- I don't want any gifts.

04:37.540 --> 04:39.479
I mean,
the party's already a lot.

04:39.579 --> 04:41.198
First of all, who are you?

04:41.298 --> 04:43.276
Second of all,
I planned something special.

04:43.376 --> 04:45.075
So can you make an exception
for your big sis?

04:45.175 --> 04:46.874
Fine.

04:46.974 --> 04:48.833
But can we at least tell people

04:48.933 --> 04:50.513
to donate to a cause
I care about,

04:50.613 --> 04:51.912
like Black Girls Rock?

04:52.012 --> 04:53.751
Of course, baby.
It's your party.

04:53.851 --> 04:55.950
Whatever you want, Ash.

04:56.050 --> 04:59.068
Well, then what I really want
is for Will to come home.

05:02.166 --> 05:04.265
I miss him.

05:17.278 --> 05:19.277
Oh, man.

05:23.315 --> 05:25.653
Shit.

05:25.753 --> 05:27.053
My bad, man.
Don't--don't let me interrupt.

05:27.153 --> 05:28.212
No worries, man.

05:28.312 --> 05:29.531
I love loud noises
when I'm praying.

05:29.631 --> 05:30.971
- Sorry, bro.
- You know, I'm just thinking.

05:31.071 --> 05:32.969
Like, after two weeks,
I thought you'd have the timing

05:33.069 --> 05:34.329
a little bit better by now,
you know?

05:34.429 --> 05:36.887
Two weeks?
Damn, it's been that long?

05:36.987 --> 05:40.206
Two weeks, three days,
and six hours.

05:40.306 --> 05:42.324
Look, man, I appreciate you
letting me staying, all right?

05:42.424 --> 05:43.804
You know,
the block feels like home.

05:43.904 --> 05:44.743
Yeah,
you're getting comfortable

05:44.743 --> 05:46.362
in these streets, though.

05:46.462 --> 05:48.001
Coming home real late at night,
2:00, 3:00 in the morning.

05:48.101 --> 05:50.000
What, I got a curfew
or something?

05:51.819 --> 05:53.398
Bro, I'm just making sure
you good, all right?

05:53.498 --> 05:54.997
I'm fine, bro.
Eat your food.

05:55.097 --> 05:56.477
You are not yourself
when you're hungry.

05:56.577 --> 05:58.556
Mm-kay.

05:58.656 --> 06:00.954
This smell good.

06:01.054 --> 06:02.673
Mm.

06:02.773 --> 06:05.272
Yo, this omelet is low key
better than my mama's.

06:05.372 --> 06:06.871
But don't you ever,
ever repeat that.

06:06.971 --> 06:08.250
Shit, they ain't touching
my mum's cheese eggs, though.

06:08.250 --> 06:09.630
That's all I know.
- Oh.

06:10.689 --> 06:12.148
Oh, shit.

06:12.248 --> 06:14.187
Um, bro, put that in
the fridge for me, all right?

06:14.287 --> 06:15.826
I'ma get it when I come back.

06:17.765 --> 06:19.744
<i>♪ OK, big dial,
dripping hella Benjamins ♪</i>

06:19.844 --> 06:21.183
<i>♪ Never tip balls ♪</i>

06:21.283 --> 06:22.303
<i>♪ Keep it swinging
like a pendulum ♪</i>

06:22.403 --> 06:23.822
<i>♪ Never took a loss ♪</i>

06:23.922 --> 06:25.541
<i>♪ Dropping bombs
on your friend and them ♪</i>

06:25.641 --> 06:26.580
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

06:27.960 --> 06:30.338
You know, uh,

06:30.438 --> 06:32.697
I don't know, my parents are
a little worried about you.

06:32.797 --> 06:34.056
Tell them not to be.

06:34.156 --> 06:37.494
I've been out here,
uh, you know, thriving.

06:37.594 --> 06:39.493
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

06:39.593 --> 06:43.371
Matter of fact,
this is for you, my brother.

06:43.471 --> 06:46.529
Oh.
- Whoa, hey, what?

06:46.629 --> 06:48.408
Yo, what is that for?

06:48.508 --> 06:49.888
Just paying you back.

06:49.988 --> 06:51.367
OK, look, now I'm worried.

06:51.467 --> 06:53.246
What the hell
are you into, Will?

06:53.346 --> 06:54.565
Look, not every dollar
in my pocket

06:54.665 --> 06:55.884
has to come from Uncle Phil.

06:55.984 --> 06:57.643
Now, go buy yourself
something nice.

06:57.743 --> 07:00.162
Yeah, but you also can't
live with Jazz forever, either.

07:00.262 --> 07:02.161
Shit, I got more options
than you think.

07:02.261 --> 07:03.560
Why are you being so cryptic?

07:03.660 --> 07:04.999
Look, it just means that

07:05.099 --> 07:06.399
all the shit
that went down with Lou,

07:06.499 --> 07:08.238
I don't need anybody
trying to control my life.

07:08.338 --> 07:10.396
Shit, I'm my own man now.

07:15.534 --> 07:17.353
<i>♪ Yeah, it's like déjà vu ♪</i>

07:17.453 --> 07:18.952
<i>♪ I see it all the time ♪</i>

07:21.211 --> 07:22.470
