by association?

10:44.100 --> 10:46.759
Like, second-hand cool?
Like, cool once removed?

10:46.859 --> 10:48.438
I'm already regretting it.

10:48.538 --> 10:49.557
No, I just think
it's ironic that

10:49.657 --> 10:50.637
you need me to fit in
at Bel-Air,

10:50.737 --> 10:52.396
but, you know, I got you.

10:52.496 --> 10:53.355
Hey, Carlton.

10:53.455 --> 10:54.795
Hey.

10:58.093 --> 11:01.271
